ea professional applicants online application including a resume and series of short essays we now require letters of recommendation for our non stanford applicants we encourage you to select references that can speak to your entrepreneurial ambitions please do not request updates regarding your application status or materials you will be contacted directly if your application is not complete or the admissions committee requires additional information cancellation policy out of consideration for those on the waiting list and in order to send program materials in advance we have established the following cancellation policy before december 31 2011 the tuition balance may be refunded minus a $1500 cancellation fee no refund if cancellation is after december 31 2011 nonpayment of fee does not constitute cancellation written notification is required back to top admissions faculty & research alumni recruiters & companies giving executive education news about the gsb copyright 2012 stanford graduate school of business site help terms of use & policies stanford university
